{"tid":2045761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被控警車上以頭撞警　24 歲男襲警罪不成立　官指警非可靠證人","createTime":"2020-06-01T04:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T04:31:53.000Z","uid":275425,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2b24ed52c06ee2654996615c422d32b1369c32","tid":2045761,"uid":275425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:05:18.000Z","msg":"成個連登淨係掛住幫侵連任，手足都唔理。<br />\n<br />\n//去年 8 月 3 日晚至翌日凌晨，黃大仙發生警民衝突。一名 24 歲男青年被指於警車內以頭撞傷警員。裁判官鍾明新今裁定被告罪名不成立，並指報稱受襲的警員並非誠實可靠證人。<br />\n<br />\n鍾鍾明新指如案發經過是如警員所指，被告解開安全帶後用頭撞他，他再聯同其他警員將被告壓制在他大腿上，期間被告頭部「周圍 fing」的話，被告的頭部不可能受到如此嚴重的瘀傷及流大量鼻血，故認為警員並非誠實可靠證人。考慮到控方案情依賴警員單方面證供，認為控方舉證未能達致毫無合理疑點，裁定被告襲警罪名不成立。//"},{"pid":"00863f38e4b0740faf05d75a119d7baece9bb15e","tid":2045761,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"個官大獲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得罪左皇軍 好快變空中飛人/浮屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d50cf2d4f66e0cd9816feabe56a8f2c395f537","tid":2045761,"uid":225362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"即係俾假口供？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848310b137e2263d35ae3ed92b556154404d0f9c","tid":2045761,"uid":272371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"//被告的頭部不可能受到如此嚴重的瘀傷及流大量鼻血//<br />\n又係用私刑"},{"pid":"30c71fac4dec5d58375c20bf60a50cfe225e5a51","tid":2045761,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f2d50cf2d4f66e0cd9816feabe56a8f2c395f537","tid":2045761,"uid":225362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"即係俾假口供？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"so? 告得入係